social_posts.post_text: 2022 Flew by and loved every moment of it 🤙🏻

Personally the Big Spoon is my favorite 🥄
What’s yours?
Antelope canyon ultra was full of views and rain. Had a blast. Good times with some good peeps 🤙🏻
Got my first Mountain bike race in today and didn’t die 🤣 Cheers to a good year yall 💪🏻
And that’s a wrap on the year. Cheers to the best one yet and bringing on 40 with a bang. Loved every minute of it and all of y’all that had a part of my life.
Coming up on 5 years of fitness at @theirongames with some great memories Lesssssss gooooo 💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻
Hero WOD Horton today with babe. 💕
Non motivational quote of the day… “Your life can’t fall apart if you never had it together” 🤣
A little bit of this a little bit of that in Prescott. All I know is that we ran far, finished and had a blast. Man vs Horse 2023 🤙🏻
My Christmas card for the year. Was easier to post it than mail it to all yall. Happy holidays and love ya!

2023 was for sure full of some wild times. From tons of day trips, my first Trail Ultra, Triathlon and Mountain bike race, a couple of hospital visits 🤣 Nashville for my 40th, crossfit comps and everything else I could fit in. Bring on 2024!
